headline: MAYBELLINE NEW YORK NAMED FIRST-EVER OFFICIAL COSMETICS PARTNER OF WWE®
summary: WWE, part of TKO Group Holdings, and Maybelline New York, the number one cosmetic brand in the world, announced today a new partnership in which the beauty brand will become the first-ever Official Cosmetics Partner of WWE.
